<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="by-all-means">by all means</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-of-course">1.<strong>尽一切办法；务必；[表示答应] 当然可以（of course）：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please by all means hand in the report on time. 
请务必准时上交报告。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Can I use your car? 
我能用你的汽车吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— By all means. 
当然。</p></div></div>